                    <span>If you've been wondering what Sylvie has been up to these many years, wonder no more. The introduction alone is worth the price of the book--a humbling lesson in how much care is needed in using a language.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A Presbyterian Summa</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
